resources.string: faatagaina oe i ala le togafiti i faʻalua tapping i le screen.

faatagaina oe i sosoʻo USB masini. a faagaoioia ese togafiti e fesootai i ai USB galuega tauave, e pei e pei ADB ma MTP, o le a lē ona iai seʻi lea o tagata gase poʻo le togafiti o rebooted. lē uma USB masini o le a galulue.
Faaopoopoga le alofaʻaga a le paʻi pupuni ina paʻi mafai ona faamauina aʻo ofuina totigilima.
e mafai ai ona le tulaga lua sim pepa malō slot. lea e tatau lē ona faagaoioia seia vagana i ai o se sim pepa malō i le tulaga lua slot. (Manaomia Reboot!)

O lenei galuega solo mataupu i Snapchat, Instagram ma ese vitio puʻega apps. faaaogaina le google avc encoder nai lo a le hw avc encoder. oe Mae manaomia i restart le polokalama poʻo restart le togafiti aʻo leʻi lea faatulagaga e aafiaga. lea Mae foʻi ala se vitio puʻega apps lē i galulue.
E le lagolagoina i lea masini...
Faafetai oe uma mo oe lagolagoina!
